                        <p
                          id="fs-idm193932640"
                        >As required, the overall reaction is the same for both the two-step uncatalyzed mechanism and the three-step NO-catalyzed mechanism:</p>
                        <div data-type="equation" id="fs-idm46801248">
                          <math display="block">
                            <semantics>
                              <mrow>
                                <mrow>
                                  <mn>2</mn>
                                  <msub>
                                    <mtext>O</mtext>
                                    <mn>3</mn>
                                  </msub>
                                  <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>
                                  <mi>g</mi>
                                  <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>
                                  <mspace width="0.2em"/>
